* How to install extensions to heroku
Heroku does not handle submodules, and extensions are installed as git submodules -> there are not pushed correctly to heroku
Here is how to remove the submodule, then we just have to add the files to the main repo
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/894647/radiant-extensions-on-heroku
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1260748/how-do-i-remove-a-git-submodule

